{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·006.1", "text_original": "有兔爰爰，雉離于羅。我生之初，尚無為。我生之後，逢此百罹，尚寐無吪？", "text_normalized": "有兔爰爰，雉離于羅。我生之初，尚無為。我生之後，逢此百罹，尚寐無吪？", "notes": "兔爰 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·006.2", "text_original": "有兔爰爰，雉離于罦。我生之初，尚無造。我生之後，逢此百憂，尚寐無覺？", "text_normalized": "有兔爰爰，雉離于罦。我生之初，尚無造。我生之後，逢此百憂，尚寐無覺？", "notes": "兔爰 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-wangfeng-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-wangfeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·王風·006.3", "text_original": "有兔爰爰，雉離于罿。我生之初，尚無庸。我生之後，逢此百凶，尚寐無聦！", "text_normalized": "有兔爰爰，雉離于罿。我生之初，尚無庸。我生之後，逢此百凶，尚寐無聦！", "notes": "兔爰 Chinese stanza 3."}
